revision.text: Possibly: [Eustathiou Archiepiskopou Thessalonikēs Parekbolai eis tēn Homērou Iliada kai Odysseian meta euporōtatou kai pany ōphelimou pinakos] = Eustathii Archiepiscopi Thessalonicae In Homeri Iliadis et Odysseae libros [parekbolai], indice adiuncto perutili & copioso, by Eustathius, Archbishop of Thessalonica, d. ca. 1194. (Basileae : [Froben], 1559-1560.) http://library.st-andrews.ac.uk/record=b1447177~S1
